{"tid":1458701,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日機場所感, 有d 提議","createTime":"2019-08-12T14:44:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T16:14:59.000Z","uid":57439,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7be0479b5e739eb25a7e891ccf53ea39b2482ce1","tid":1458701,"uid":57439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:44:36.000Z","msg":"大家都係希望俾旅客知香港人訴求, 但係大堂到叫口號, 聲音好散, 真係未必聽到, 不如友善出擊<br />\n<br />\n尤其當航班取消時, 好多旅客都panic, 不知所措, 自己試下主動接觸旅客, 一黎佢地會安心d, 二黎順手解釋下我地做緊乜<br />\n<br />\n今日幫左幾批大陸客, 其中一個明明好嬲, 係路邊大鬧<br />\n<br />\n自己行過去了解下, 原來機場接送果d 垃圾司機, 踢左佢落車先通知話flight cxl, 根本唔知可以點<br />\n<br />\n話陪佢去airline 到問未來安排, 佢話根本行唔到去櫃台<br />\n<br />\n一邊安撫一邊解釋我地全部都好有禮貌 (亦多謝手足讓路)<br />\n<br />\n最後搞清楚真係無機, 再指路叫佢去機場酒店, 同時態度亦明顯軟化, 淨係ee 哦哦話唔係唔可以表達, 只係應該和平d<br />\n<br />\n其他旅客都係千多謝萬多謝, 如果對方反應ok, 再順勢sell 下五大訴求, 好多人都buy<br />\n<br />\n希望有手足一齊做下旅客親善大使<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5552c98d26a027ec7c5ad479cb2ca859a59f6f2","tid":1458701,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:45:22.000Z","msg":"[賽後檢討] 抗爭者進化史<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1458526\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1458526</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a3e6851a15d7212e7ddb0ea56f115c7343eb75ed","tid":1458701,"uid":57439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:47:51.000Z","msg":"自推#1"},{"pid":"22aa6412ed6ba315f24ba57b2a0ffdaca2e68d6d","tid":1458701,"uid":295188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:51:13.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"4eec90d4f9ea9e62c2db0e994fb428fcfd7920b3","tid":1458701,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:01:12.000Z","msg":"pushhhhhh"},{"pid":"1aee1bc2ee1deb660a6fc9ff60360e883cfe829e","tid":1458701,"uid":57439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"